import React from 'react'

const ListQuestion = (l) => {
    console.log(l)
  return (
    <>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <th scope="row">{l.prop.questionDetail}</th>
      
      <button className='btn btn-warning'>edit</button>
     <button className='btn btn-warm'>delete</button>
     
    </tr>
    </tbody>
    
    </>
  )
}

export default ListQuestion
